            "Bought 10 shares of GOOGL at $142.71\n",
            "Portfolio value = 10009.10, Cash= 7154.90, Holdings: AAPL = 0 shares, GOOGL = 20 shares\n",
            "User Bob:\n",
            "Bought 15 shares of GOOGL at $142.71\n",
            "Portfolio value = 10050.55, Cash= 2969.95, Holdings: AAPL = 15 shares, GOOGL = 30 shares\n",
            "User Charlie:\n",
            "Bought 5 shares of GOOGL at $142.71\n",
            "Portfolio value = 10004.55, Cash= 8577.45, Holdings: AAPL = 0 shares, GOOGL = 10 shares\n",
            "\n",
